body_html:
@johnyquest7 Kindly open an issue on the tfcoreml repo and close this one.

Meanwhile,

  • can you update the tfcoreml to latest master and see if you still get the same error message
  • The error is raised while converting the op named "module_apply_default/cell_stem_1/strided_slice". Can you execute the .pb graph and get the inputs and outputs of this op? That way we can find the configuration in which this op is being used. This would tell whether there is a bug in the converter or this particular configuration of strided slice is not supported by CoreML.

body:
@johnyquest7 Kindly open an issue on the [tfcoreml](https://github.com/tf-coreml/tf-coreml) repo and close this one. 

Meanwhile, 
- can you update the tfcoreml to latest master and see if you still get the same error message
- The error is raised while converting the op named "module_apply_default/cell_stem_1/strided_slice". Can you execute the .pb graph and get the inputs and outputs of this op? That way we can find the configuration in which this op is being used. This would tell whether there is a bug in the converter or this particular configuration of strided slice is not supported by CoreML.
